responseText: NSLOCTEXT("", "FAED98D64A92B47CAF6D4E8FD05BC84A", "Many thanks, kind sir. I would not have fared well against those terrorizing toadstools. It\'s quite peculiar that I often find them existing in the same regions as ancient impacts. Peculiar indeed. ")
